data.description: Check this 6 bedroom home out! With 6 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, there is enough space for everyone! This west side home (with a pool) is in the perfect home for you! The downstairs features a formal dining, separate living area, master bedroom with en suite bath & an additional half bathroom (recently remodeled). The upstairs boasts 5 spacious bedrooms with an additional 2 full bathrooms. Outside you'll find a spacious side yard, large backyard with a great pool & plenty of space for all of your friends and family! Solar panels are a huge added bonus; assumed at only 1.9%, they are cheaper than paying the electric company & can save you hundreds every month. Call the listing agents with any questions.
